{"tid":1199193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港加油 四字已成中共禁詞","createTime":"2019-06-10T12:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T17:18:25.000Z","uid":54373,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f9fcf5d243dab1160030067b06f97b4a85caf067","tid":1199193,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:09:58.000Z","msg":"在微博搜索「香港加油」、「支持香港」，均會出現「根據相關法律法規和政策，『香港加油／支持香港』搜索結果未予顯示」的結果；至於輸入「反送中」，則沒有搜索結果出現。但「加油香港」、「撐香港」、「香港支持」等詞卻沒有被封禁。<br />\n<br />\n「香港加油」成微博禁詞的原因未明，不過，可能與海外華人遊行時，高呼「撐香港，反送中，香港加油！」的口號有關。此外，台灣行政院長蘇貞昌等政治人物在Facebook 發文聲援香港遊行時，也加入了「香港加油」的主題標籤"},{"pid":"c73d63a5273d1b4f49e5022ba4c4383ffbb0d7cd","tid":1199193,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:11:30.000Z","msg":"沉得好快"},{"pid":"4098d354d1e850027778d8136f32fcb8f41f3447","tid":1199193,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:12:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2c4f2e043fe995858ed42b1ccaead9b2afcc9f9","tid":1199193,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"95027f51cfb9339e1532d646abca54533265e4b5","tid":1199193,"uid":221666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:14:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33613d9cca3facb1e8c0061bcd0876ebd3517ce3","tid":1199193,"uid":70227,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:20:27.000Z","msg":"執柒全國互聯網<br />\n鎖國只俾上內聯網啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31369aae972c205295fea4e04479702b6612a1d2","tid":1199193,"uid":209978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:22:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a26b6f2705851e3407e4c58fdf107d5d394453ba","tid":1199193,"uid":230890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:22:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41396f51a97e009127190c4c2cc52e79340b45cf","tid":1199193,"uid":17008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1